manifest.name: Notemd
manifest.description: Enhances notes using LLMs: 1) Processes text to add [[wiki-links]] and create concept notes. 2) Performs web research (Tavily/DuckDuckGo) and summarizes topics. 3) Generates content from note titles. Supports multiple LLM providers and customizable output.
manifest.author: jacob
